short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get to the Elden Ring Wiki faster

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Barebones shortcut for searching on the FextraLife Elden Ring Wiki. Clicking the extension icon or using the keyboard shortcut "Alt+Q" brings you directly to the wiki and focuses the search bar.
